data.title: Activ Business Casimcea Wind Farm
data.text: The Activ Business Casimcea Wind Farm is a proposed wind power project in Casimcea, Tulcea County, Romania. It will have 13 individual wind turbines[1] with a nominal output of around 3.46 MW which will deliver up to 45 MW of power, enough to power over 28,450 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$80 million.
